OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FTwo sisters devastated by the hit-and-
OL,7,Frun death of their father in West
OL,8,FBelfast are campaigning for a change
OL,9,Fin the law in hopes that other
OL,10,Fchildren of a parent killed on our
OL,11,Froads may get the support they never
OL,12,Fdid.
OL,14,FSpeaking to UTV, the daughters shared
OL,15,Fthe grief they continue to carry after
OL,16,Fall these years without a dad to see
OL,17,Ftheir own little ones.
OL,19,FShauneen Butler spoke about the day
OL,20,Fshe found out her dad had died.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FShe said: "My brothers were screaming,
OL,7,Fbreaking down.
OL,9,F"My aunties and uncles in the doorway,
OL,10,Fjust all looking in as we're being
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,F"And then I feel like we were just so
OL,14,Fconfused, cause what was death? Our
OL,15,Ffirst experience of death was this."
OL,17,FShauneen Butler was just eight years
OL,18,Fold when she and her siblings, the
OL,19,Fyoungest just five, were told their
OL,20,Ffather Cornelius had been killed in a
OL,21,Fhit-and-run.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FShauneen continued: "Flash forward to
OL,7,Feven finding out he's coming home.
OL,9,F"I was like, 'Oh my god, Daddy's
OL,10,Fcoming home! I heard Daddy's coming
OL,11,Fhome!' And I got on my bike.
OL,13,F"Same with all of our friends. We all
OL,14,Fgot on our bikes and we're racing, and
OL,15,Fthen we seen the hearse.
OL,17,F"The hearse comes into the cul-de-sac
OL,18,Fand we kind of just parked the bike up
OL,19,Fbeside the lamp post and staring at
OL,20,Fit, and it's the fact to this day, I
OL,21,Fcan't handle death."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FThis tragedy dates back almost 25
OL,7,Fyears to a September night in West
OL,8,FBelfast.
OL,10,FCornelius, or "Con" as he was known,
OL,11,Fhad just finished his shift at a bar
OL,12,Fon the Springfield Road and was
OL,13,Fwalking home when he was knocked down
OL,14,Fand killed in a hit-and-run.
OL,16,FFast forward to 2026, and his loved
OL,17,Fones are campaigning for change.
OL,19,FButler's Law is the endgame of that
OL,20,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FTo force those responsible for killing
OL,7,Fa parent due to drink, drugs, or in a
OL,8,Fhit-and-run, to pay ongoing financial
OL,9,Fsupport for any children left behind.
OL,11,FThis would be separate to anything
OL,12,Fthat currently exists in the courts.
OL,14,FShauneen says she feels "like it could
OL,15,Fhelp so many families. Families that
OL,16,Fhaven't even been through this yet.
OL,17,FNobody knows what tomorrow holds. And
OL,18,Fif there was something in place like
OL,19,Fthis, it could help deter people."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,FSince Cornelius was killed, many
OL,7,Fchildren have lost a parent on our
OL,8,Froads.
OL,10,FIt's a long journey ahead with tens of
OL,11,Fthousands of signatures needed just to
OL,12,Fget this debated in Parliament but
OL,13,Fthese daughters have a strong resolve.
OL,15,FShauneen said: "If somebody else takes
OL,16,Fthat wee baton and runs with it`if
OL,17,Fwe're walking so somebody else can
OL,18,Fcome along and run with it`I'm more
OL,19,Fthan happy with that.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776438666
OL,3,CSisters campaign for law to support
OL,4,Cchildren of road victims
OL,6,F"This isn't about us at all. This is
OL,7,Fjust us sharing our story, so it's
OL,8,Fabout other children."
